data.description: Are you looking for your own primary residence or to add to your investment portfolio? Check out this CUTE 2 bedroom, 1 bath bungalow that is located in an area in downtown Brunswick that is undergoing a lot of revitalization and NO FLOOD insurance is required! The front porch has been enclosed for additional living space. Inside you will find a freshly painted interior and a big open living area with wood flooring. The Eat in kitchen is fully equipped with all appliances, white tile counter tops, wood cabinetry and a nice wood laminate flooring. There is also an area perfect for a coffee bar. A nicely remodeled tiled bathroom with new PVC main sewage line separates the two bedrooms that also have wood flooring. This home offers a spacious laundry room and an additional room that could be used as a home office, gym or as a storage room. It is located just off of the kitchen and laundry room with easy access to the backyard. This room has its own separate Smart heating/cooling system. Fenced back yard, detached storage building and a Single covered carport with paved parking pad complete this home. Close to downtown so you can enjoy many great restaurants, shops and activities and it is just a short walk to the Brunswick Landing Marina and a quick 15 minute drive to our beautiful beaches! ***This property qualifies for special loan programs which could include a discounted interest rate (possibly up to 2%) or 100% financing with NO PMI for qualified buyers.***
